1
00:01:25,472 --> 00:01:29,792
=Lost You Forever S2=

2
00:01:30,192 --> 00:01:32,720
=Episode 11=

3
00:01:35,594 --> 00:01:36,874
Once, I was starving.

4
00:01:38,075 --> 00:01:39,075
One of my heads

5
00:01:41,008 --> 00:01:41,594
almost

6
00:01:41,594 --> 00:01:43,155
ate another one.

7
00:01:47,194 --> 00:01:47,954
Really?

8
00:01:52,035 --> 00:01:52,634
No.

9
00:01:53,155 --> 00:01:53,834
You...

10
00:01:56,995 --> 00:01:59,115
Someone once told me

11
00:02:01,234 --> 00:02:02,634
that humans are strange.

12
00:02:03,675 --> 00:02:05,115
They have to figure out

13
00:02:05,395 --> 00:02:06,715
if they're happy or in pain

14
00:02:07,715 --> 00:02:09,355
through comparison with others.

15
00:02:11,155 --> 00:02:12,034
So I told you

16
00:02:12,034 --> 00:02:14,914
about my miserable past
for your comparison

17
00:02:15,634 --> 00:02:16,795
so that you realize

18
00:02:17,155 --> 00:02:19,075
that you're just fine.

19
00:02:20,114 --> 00:02:21,595
But I didn't lie.

20
00:02:24,274 --> 00:02:26,114
I did crawl out of an egg.

21
00:02:27,834 --> 00:02:29,114
I don't know my parents.

22
00:02:30,034 --> 00:02:31,795
I do have nine heads.

23
00:02:33,435 --> 00:02:34,315
As for the rest...

24
00:02:36,274 --> 00:02:37,274
As for the rest,

25
00:02:38,674 --> 00:02:39,754
I got carried away.

26
00:02:42,674 --> 00:02:44,075
What did I say?

27
00:02:50,435 --> 00:02:52,034
Do you need me to tell you more

28
00:02:52,034 --> 00:02:53,595
about my tragic past

29
00:02:54,315 --> 00:02:55,435
to make you think

30
00:02:56,155 --> 00:02:57,634
that having a devil as a father

31
00:02:57,634 --> 00:02:58,875
is actually not so bad?

32
00:03:00,634 --> 00:03:01,634
No need.

33
00:03:05,754 --> 00:03:06,834
Be it you deities,

34
00:03:06,834 --> 00:03:07,955
or we demons,

35
00:03:10,435 --> 00:03:11,995
no one can choose their origin.

36
00:03:14,834 --> 00:03:15,595
So,

37
00:03:16,595 --> 00:03:18,114
why get hung up on something

38
00:03:18,114 --> 00:03:19,394
that happened before you were born?

39
00:03:27,754 --> 00:03:29,955
Hong Jiang was Chenrong's general.

40
00:03:30,515 --> 00:03:31,795
When you followed him,

41
00:03:32,634 --> 00:03:33,914
did you see Chi Chen?

42
00:03:37,795 --> 00:03:38,384
No.

43
00:03:40,674 --> 00:03:42,355
Chi Chen had died before I followed

44
00:03:44,155 --> 00:03:45,274
my foster father.

45
00:03:46,995 --> 00:03:48,834
It's said that Chi Chen was cunning

46
00:03:50,795 --> 00:03:51,955
and heartless.

47
00:03:53,795 --> 00:03:54,914
But why did he

48
00:03:54,914 --> 00:03:56,554
insist on taking the path

49
00:03:58,315 --> 00:03:59,875
that was a dead end?

50
00:04:02,315 --> 00:04:04,355
The war lasted for over 100 years

51
00:04:05,674 --> 00:04:06,674
with huge casualties.

52
00:04:09,875 --> 00:04:10,795
Perhaps,

53
00:04:12,595 --> 00:04:14,634
rather than living in pain
and mourning for

54
00:04:14,634 --> 00:04:15,554
his people,

55
00:04:17,954 --> 00:04:19,035
it was better to die.

56
00:04:24,875 --> 00:04:26,234
For a general,

57
00:04:27,035 --> 00:04:28,315
the best end

58
00:04:30,794 --> 00:04:31,995
is to die in battle.

59
00:04:39,674 --> 00:04:40,475
What about you?

60
00:04:42,234 --> 00:04:43,794
Why did you choose Hong Jiang?

61
00:04:46,834 --> 00:04:48,954
Just because he was your foster father?

62
00:04:52,595 --> 00:04:53,755
It's not just that.

63
00:04:54,715 --> 00:04:55,954
There were also those who had

64
00:04:58,475 --> 00:04:59,995
fought alongside me.

65
00:05:01,554 --> 00:05:02,755
We fought together,

66
00:05:04,755 --> 00:05:05,674
drank together,

67
00:05:08,635 --> 00:05:10,234
and we gathered our comrades' remains.

68
00:05:13,715 --> 00:05:14,755
It's been centuries.

69
00:05:16,554 --> 00:05:18,554
Their bodies
have long since turned to dust.

70
00:05:25,114 --> 00:05:26,155
But I have nine heads.

71
00:05:28,435 --> 00:05:30,475
It's impossible to forget something.

72
00:05:32,554 --> 00:05:33,234
Even now,

73
00:05:34,514 --> 00:05:36,074
I remember their voices

74
00:05:39,755 --> 00:05:40,834
and faces.

75
00:05:47,435 --> 00:05:49,155
My mother once told me

76
00:05:50,394 --> 00:05:52,234
that there are things we must hold on to

77
00:05:53,475 --> 00:05:54,954
even at the cost

78
00:05:56,595 --> 00:05:57,875
of our lives.

79
00:05:59,475 --> 00:06:01,954
Fourth Uncle abandoned
Auntie and Cang Xuan.

80
00:06:04,234 --> 00:06:05,554
My mother abandoned me.

81
00:06:07,674 --> 00:06:09,435
If they were not my relatives,

82
00:06:10,315 --> 00:06:12,035
I would find them awe-inspiring.

83
00:06:15,354 --> 00:06:16,954
But as a daughter,

84
00:06:19,514 --> 00:06:21,794
no matter how awe-inspiring
my mother might be,

85
00:06:25,155 --> 00:06:26,635
I don't want to forgive her.

86
00:08:46,995 --> 00:08:48,114
What are you doing?

87
00:09:05,594 --> 00:09:06,995
Tushan Jing.

88
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:18,384
(Slaying mighty foes)

89
00:09:25,395 --> 00:09:26,234
Xiaoyao.

90
00:09:26,755 --> 00:09:27,914
Take a closer look.

91
00:09:35,024 --> 00:09:39,408
(Annihilating the nobles,
Protecting the Central Plains)

92
00:09:43,696 --> 00:09:48,336
(Assuming great responsibility,
Abandoning personal feelings)

93
00:09:52,208 --> 00:09:56,784
(Living up to the expectations
of the people and their loved ones)

94
00:10:16,594 --> 00:10:17,635
I believe

95
00:10:18,794 --> 00:10:20,714
that Xiang Liu's speculation
is the truth.

96
00:10:22,755 --> 00:10:24,995
Your father did not betray your mother.

97
00:10:27,234 --> 00:10:28,674
Nor did your mother

98
00:10:28,674 --> 00:10:29,875
let your father down.

99
00:10:32,234 --> 00:10:33,034
It's just

100
00:10:33,474 --> 00:10:35,354
that as the great general of Chenrong,

101
00:10:36,635 --> 00:10:38,275
and the general of Xiyan,

102
00:10:39,515 --> 00:10:42,034
they had no choice in that chaotic era.

103
00:10:42,288 --> 00:10:44,240
(Abandoning personal feelings)

104
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,416
(Living up to the expectations
of the people and their loved ones)

105
00:10:48,435 --> 00:10:50,075
They died

106
00:10:52,594 --> 00:10:54,955
to live up to the expectations
of the people and their loved ones.

107
00:10:59,195 --> 00:11:00,674
But they gave birth to me.

108
00:11:01,114 --> 00:11:02,755
Why didn't they raise me?

109
00:11:06,075 --> 00:11:07,594
Before they died,

110
00:11:09,234 --> 00:11:11,315
didn't they think of me?

111
00:11:13,594 --> 00:11:15,635
Weren't they worried

112
00:11:16,474 --> 00:11:18,714
that I would be hunted down,

113
00:11:19,515 --> 00:11:21,435
become homeless,

114
00:11:22,554 --> 00:11:24,395
and be tormented in a cage

115
00:11:24,395 --> 00:11:27,315
by a nine-tailed fox?

116
00:12:33,515 --> 00:12:34,154
Xuan.

117
00:12:34,554 --> 00:12:35,354
I'm back.

118
00:12:35,835 --> 00:12:36,594
Is it cold outside?

119
00:12:36,755 --> 00:12:38,320
I asked Miao Pu to make you
some chicken soup.

120
00:12:38,474 --> 00:12:39,635
Have it to warm yourself up.

121
00:12:39,875 --> 00:12:40,395
No need.

122
00:12:40,875 --> 00:12:41,714
It's not very cold.

123
00:12:43,474 --> 00:12:44,635
Head back and have a rest.

124
00:12:44,835 --> 00:12:45,755
Don't worry about me.

125
00:12:46,195 --> 00:12:46,794
I'm fine.

126
00:12:49,435 --> 00:12:49,955
Princess.

127
00:12:50,154 --> 00:12:51,075
Have some hot soup.

128
00:12:54,234 --> 00:12:55,075
I deserve to die.

129
00:12:59,435 --> 00:13:00,594
You don't deserve to die.

130
00:13:02,435 --> 00:13:03,395
I do.

131
00:13:05,955 --> 00:13:07,914
Don't call me Princess anymore.

132
00:13:13,914 --> 00:13:14,755
Remove the chessboard.

133
00:13:15,794 --> 00:13:16,995
And bring some wine.

134
00:13:17,554 --> 00:13:18,195
Yes.

135
00:13:29,875 --> 00:13:30,515
Princess,

136
00:13:31,435 --> 00:13:32,154
it's getting late.

137
00:13:32,435 --> 00:13:33,234
Have a drink.

138
00:13:36,835 --> 00:13:37,995
You know I'm not a princess.

139
00:13:39,034 --> 00:13:40,034
But you're joining them

140
00:13:40,034 --> 00:13:40,835
to bully me?

141
00:13:41,154 --> 00:13:42,594
Why aren't you a princess?

142
00:13:43,275 --> 00:13:44,794
Tomorrow, I can appoint you

143
00:13:44,955 --> 00:13:46,395
as the Princess of Xiyan.

144
00:13:47,195 --> 00:13:48,594
Let alone a princess,

145
00:13:48,594 --> 00:13:49,435
you can be a lord

146
00:13:49,435 --> 00:13:50,794
if you want to.

147
00:13:52,075 --> 00:13:53,195
Feel free to pick a spot

148
00:13:53,234 --> 00:13:54,114
under my reign.

149
00:13:54,154 --> 00:13:54,875
It will be yours.

150
00:13:55,914 --> 00:13:56,474
Xuan.

151
00:13:57,154 --> 00:13:58,594
Can you stop making trouble?

152
00:14:05,835 --> 00:14:07,674
Do you really care
whether you are a princess?

153
00:14:10,315 --> 00:14:11,234
You know very well

154
00:14:11,995 --> 00:14:14,256
that I don't care about the identity,

155
00:14:14,256 --> 00:14:14,835
but...

156
00:14:14,835 --> 00:14:16,554
You care that Auntie deceived you

157
00:14:16,554 --> 00:14:18,195
over and over again.

158
00:14:21,554 --> 00:14:23,395
Auntie promised to go back to you

159
00:14:23,955 --> 00:14:25,154
but she never did.

160
00:14:26,075 --> 00:14:27,515
Auntie knew who your father was,

161
00:14:27,515 --> 00:14:29,114
but never told you the truth.

162
00:14:30,075 --> 00:14:32,075
Even though they were

163
00:14:32,075 --> 00:14:33,075
your own parents,

164
00:14:33,674 --> 00:14:35,474
you knew nothing about

165
00:14:35,995 --> 00:14:37,075
their past.

166
00:14:41,835 --> 00:14:43,315
I have always wondered

167
00:14:45,275 --> 00:14:48,034
who dared to seal
the Rejuvenating Flower

168
00:14:48,195 --> 00:14:49,914
within me,

169
00:14:50,714 --> 00:14:52,794
making me a faceless person.

170
00:14:55,234 --> 00:14:56,554
It turned out to be my mother.

171
00:14:59,114 --> 00:15:01,034
She wanted to hide my appearance.

172
00:15:03,635 --> 00:15:06,114
She even tried to
deceive me about my looks.

173
00:15:19,315 --> 00:15:22,794
Both our mothers are heartless.

174
00:15:25,955 --> 00:15:27,315
Do you still hate your mother?

175
00:15:31,794 --> 00:15:33,075
Not anymore.

176
00:15:36,034 --> 00:15:37,354
But I often dream of her

177
00:15:37,354 --> 00:15:38,835
committing suicide before my eyes.

178
00:15:42,554 --> 00:15:44,835
I've become the ruler of a kingdom.

179
00:15:47,315 --> 00:15:49,835
But whenever I wake up from a nightmare,

180
00:15:51,195 --> 00:15:52,835
I still feel helpless

181
00:15:54,474 --> 00:15:55,354
and desperate.

182
00:15:58,714 --> 00:15:59,594
Me too.

183
00:16:07,755 --> 00:16:09,154
Every time I dream of my mother,

184
00:16:10,755 --> 00:16:12,674
no matter how happy it starts,

185
00:16:14,794 --> 00:16:16,034
in the end,

186
00:16:17,315 --> 00:16:19,515
I always see her in her armor

187
00:16:19,515 --> 00:16:20,955
walking away from me.

188
00:16:22,794 --> 00:16:25,554
I always call out to her from behind.

189
00:16:25,554 --> 00:16:27,315
No matter how loudly I shout,

190
00:16:28,395 --> 00:16:29,515
she keeps walking away

191
00:16:30,995 --> 00:16:32,034
and never turns back.

192
00:16:33,114 --> 00:16:35,315
People think that Princess General

193
00:16:35,714 --> 00:16:37,075
chose righteousness over life.

194
00:16:37,914 --> 00:16:39,354
But the image of her

195
00:16:40,674 --> 00:16:42,315
walking away with her back at me

196
00:16:44,114 --> 00:16:46,315
is a life-long pain for me.

197
00:16:47,395 --> 00:16:48,794
People think

198
00:16:50,794 --> 00:16:54,275
that my mother had a deep affection
for my father and followed him

199
00:16:55,195 --> 00:16:56,474
to the afterworld.

200
00:16:58,914 --> 00:17:01,594
But what I couldn't get out of my mind
was the moment

201
00:17:04,434 --> 00:17:05,755
she pushed me away

202
00:17:07,515 --> 00:17:09,314
and plunged the dagger

203
00:17:10,875 --> 00:17:12,635
into her own chest.

204
00:17:16,515 --> 00:17:18,155
If she could die for my father,

205
00:17:20,314 --> 00:17:22,635
why couldn't she live for me?

206
00:17:43,555 --> 00:17:44,395
Mother.

207
00:17:46,434 --> 00:17:48,875
Mother, I don't want to
go to Mount Jade.

208
00:17:50,755 --> 00:17:53,035
I want to go home and find Xuan.

209
00:17:55,395 --> 00:17:58,035
I don't want to go to Mount Jade.

210
00:18:01,795 --> 00:18:03,035
I want to go home...

211
00:18:04,434 --> 00:18:05,395
Xuan.

212
00:18:34,635 --> 00:18:35,434
Don't be afraid.

213
00:18:37,875 --> 00:18:39,954
Your brother has grown up.

214
00:18:41,755 --> 00:18:42,675
No one can

215
00:18:42,675 --> 00:18:44,635
take you away from me.

216
00:18:47,114 --> 00:18:49,035
No one will dare to hurt you.

217
00:19:26,555 --> 00:19:27,795
This stack of memorials

218
00:19:27,995 --> 00:19:29,434
is all about the Great Princess.

219
00:19:30,515 --> 00:19:31,555
It calls for celebration.

220
00:19:32,675 --> 00:19:33,635
Haoling has been

221
00:19:34,114 --> 00:19:36,035
prosperous through proper governance.

222
00:19:36,155 --> 00:19:38,035
The ministers have nothing to do

223
00:19:38,234 --> 00:19:41,035
and can only comment
on my family affairs.

224
00:19:41,795 --> 00:19:43,234
There are rumors everywhere

225
00:19:43,344 --> 00:19:45,714
that the Great Princess disrupts
the bloodline of Haoling royal family

226
00:19:45,714 --> 00:19:46,995
and she's a disgrace to Haoling.

227
00:19:47,194 --> 00:19:49,155
They hope you can punish her severely.

228
00:19:49,194 --> 00:19:49,834
Father.

229
00:19:49,834 --> 00:19:51,314
The rumors are becoming outrageous.

230
00:19:51,434 --> 00:19:52,434
You must do something.

231
00:19:52,635 --> 00:19:53,314
Like what?

232
00:19:53,594 --> 00:19:55,114
Summon the elders of the Lirong Family

233
00:19:55,314 --> 00:19:56,354
to perform rituals on the altar

234
00:19:56,515 --> 00:19:57,594
to prove Xiaoyao's identity,

235
00:19:57,755 --> 00:19:59,434
so that those idling ministers

236
00:19:59,474 --> 00:20:00,714
stop spreading rumors.

237
00:20:01,515 --> 00:20:02,594
Good idea.

238
00:20:04,675 --> 00:20:05,275
Ru Shou.

239
00:20:05,834 --> 00:20:07,114
Why are you silent?

240
00:20:07,795 --> 00:20:08,555
Master.

241
00:20:09,434 --> 00:20:10,915
There's something fishy about this.

242
00:20:11,434 --> 00:20:13,194
Cang Xuan holds great power

243
00:20:13,314 --> 00:20:14,234
as the new king.

244
00:20:14,635 --> 00:20:15,275
How come

245
00:20:15,275 --> 00:20:16,915
he can't suppress such trivial rumors?

246
00:20:17,474 --> 00:20:18,114
That's right.

247
00:20:18,755 --> 00:20:20,155
There is something fishy.

248
00:20:20,155 --> 00:20:21,635
I don't care if it's fishy.

249
00:20:21,915 --> 00:20:22,635
Father.

250
00:20:22,635 --> 00:20:24,314
Prove that Xiaoyao is your daughter

251
00:20:24,314 --> 00:20:25,314
to make them shut up.

252
00:20:25,714 --> 00:20:26,555
I can't prove it.

253
00:20:27,795 --> 00:20:28,875
Because Xiaoyao

254
00:20:31,434 --> 00:20:33,035
is indeed not my daughter.

255
00:20:34,395 --> 00:20:35,314
How is that possible?

256
00:20:37,114 --> 00:20:37,795
Guiwen.

257
00:20:38,074 --> 00:20:39,114
Convey my decree.

258
00:20:39,795 --> 00:20:40,555
Lady Jiuyao is not

259
00:20:40,834 --> 00:20:42,555
a descendant
of the Haoling royal family.

260
00:20:42,954 --> 00:20:44,275
Proclaim to all

261
00:20:44,834 --> 00:20:47,314
that I revoke her title
and clan membership

262
00:20:47,795 --> 00:20:48,875
right now.

263
00:20:49,594 --> 00:20:50,275
Yes.

264
00:20:50,314 --> 00:20:50,834
Father.

265
00:20:50,915 --> 00:20:51,915
What are you doing?

266
00:20:51,915 --> 00:20:52,635
Even if my sister...

267
00:20:52,912 --> 00:20:54,755
Even if Xiaoyao is not
your biological daughter,

268
00:20:54,755 --> 00:20:55,675
she has been

269
00:20:55,675 --> 00:20:56,995
your daughter for years.

270
00:20:57,035 --> 00:20:58,635
Don't you feel sorry for her?

271
00:20:58,954 --> 00:20:59,995
Why are you hitting her

272
00:20:59,995 --> 00:21:00,875
when she's down

273
00:21:00,875 --> 00:21:01,995
instead of helping her?

274
00:21:02,035 --> 00:21:02,714
Nian.

275
00:21:08,275 --> 00:21:08,834
Father.

276
00:21:09,875 --> 00:21:10,795
Xiaoyao is...

277
00:21:10,795 --> 00:21:11,434
Master.

278
00:21:13,234 --> 00:21:14,114
I take my leave.

279
00:21:41,354 --> 00:21:41,995
(Heng.)

280
00:21:43,194 --> 00:21:45,395
(I didn't fail
your and Qingyang's trust.)

281
00:21:46,354 --> 00:21:47,395
(I brought up)

282
00:21:49,155 --> 00:21:50,714
(Cang Xuan very well.)

283
00:22:04,234 --> 00:22:05,035
Your Majesty.

284
00:22:05,915 --> 00:22:06,515
Your Majesty.

285
00:22:07,074 --> 00:22:08,395
What's the fuss?

286
00:22:13,234 --> 00:22:14,114
All of you, leave.

287
00:22:19,275 --> 00:22:21,434
The King of Haoling
announced that Haoling Jiuyao...

288
00:22:22,714 --> 00:22:23,280
No.

289
00:22:23,555 --> 00:22:25,635
We should address her as Jiuyao now.

