00:34:43,595 --> 00:34:44,515
Mine is more practical.

574
00:34:44,515 --> 00:34:45,434
Mine is better.

575
00:34:46,474 --> 00:34:47,515
Why are you so happy?

576
00:34:48,714 --> 00:34:50,474
Everything has been going smoothly.

577
00:34:50,755 --> 00:34:52,755
Something happy is about to happen.

578
00:34:53,075 --> 00:34:55,115
I wake up laughing from my dreams.

579
00:34:55,835 --> 00:34:56,755
What's the happy thing?

580
00:34:57,154 --> 00:34:57,954
Of course, it is

581
00:34:57,995 --> 00:34:59,536
Miss Xiaoyao and Chief Tushan's wedding.

582
00:34:59,795 --> 00:35:01,194
All those troublesome matters

583
00:35:01,355 --> 00:35:02,154
have been resolved.

584
00:35:02,315 --> 00:35:03,995
Miss Xiaoyao has nothing to worry about.

585
00:35:04,394 --> 00:35:06,434
The two of them are busy being sweet.

586
00:35:06,714 --> 00:35:08,674
They will surely
discuss the wedding soon.

587
00:35:09,275 --> 00:35:10,234
You should prepare

588
00:35:10,234 --> 00:35:10,954
her dowry now

589
00:35:11,275 --> 00:35:12,035
to not be late.

590
00:35:12,115 --> 00:35:12,914
Don't talk nonsense.

591
00:35:16,234 --> 00:35:17,515
What did I say?

592
00:35:22,416 --> 00:35:24,355
- My prescription is better.
- My prescription is better.

593
00:35:24,355 --> 00:35:24,995
Mine is better.

594
00:35:24,995 --> 00:35:25,835
Mine is practical.

595
00:35:25,874 --> 00:35:26,595
Mine is better.

596
00:35:29,115 --> 00:35:29,714
Grandfather.

597
00:35:30,194 --> 00:35:30,995
Be the judge.

598
00:35:31,315 --> 00:35:32,515
Whose prescription is better?

599
00:35:33,995 --> 00:35:35,555
You've been arguing until now.

600
00:35:35,555 --> 00:35:36,674
Haven't you realized

601
00:35:36,714 --> 00:35:39,154
that both of your prescriptions
have their shortcomings?

602
00:35:39,755 --> 00:35:41,714
The best prescription

603
00:35:41,755 --> 00:35:43,954
is not determined by
your medical skills,

604
00:35:44,194 --> 00:35:47,275
but by the patient's family.

605
00:35:47,634 --> 00:35:48,795
Wealthy families

606
00:35:49,075 --> 00:35:50,194
will use Yin's prescription.

607
00:35:50,434 --> 00:35:51,555
Poor families

608
00:35:51,674 --> 00:35:52,714
will use yours.

609
00:35:53,634 --> 00:35:55,515
It's certainly important to be cured.

610
00:35:55,795 --> 00:35:58,914
But the livelihood
of a family also matters.

611
00:35:59,795 --> 00:36:02,234
You can't cure the patient

612
00:36:02,914 --> 00:36:04,035
and let his family starve.

613
00:36:04,315 --> 00:36:04,914
Right?

614
00:36:08,555 --> 00:36:09,355
You are right.

615
00:36:11,075 --> 00:36:12,075
My patients are nobles.

616
00:36:12,755 --> 00:36:13,995
I never realized that some patients

617
00:36:14,194 --> 00:36:15,555
couldn't afford the medicine.

618
00:36:16,275 --> 00:36:19,634
I have been too focused
on using local herbs.

619
00:36:20,154 --> 00:36:22,234
A good prescription depends not only on

620
00:36:22,234 --> 00:36:23,434
the patient's financial situation,

621
00:36:23,714 --> 00:36:26,234
but also where the patient is from.

622
00:36:27,315 --> 00:36:29,515
When I was running a clinic in Haoling,

623
00:36:29,874 --> 00:36:31,755
most of my patients were fishermen.

624
00:36:32,434 --> 00:36:33,795
I gave prescriptions based on

625
00:36:33,835 --> 00:36:34,995
the Herbal Encyclopedia.

626
00:36:35,515 --> 00:36:36,355
They worked well.

627
00:36:36,634 --> 00:36:39,154
But this prescription
came from the Central Plains.

628
00:36:39,234 --> 00:36:40,914
They didn't know it
and couldn't afford it.

629
00:36:41,434 --> 00:36:43,315
So I started using local herbs.

630
00:36:43,714 --> 00:36:44,304
As expected,

631
00:36:44,515 --> 00:36:45,835
it was much more popular

632
00:36:45,835 --> 00:36:46,674
than the previous ones.

633
00:36:48,595 --> 00:36:49,714
The natural environment

634
00:36:50,355 --> 00:36:52,115
varies throughout Dahuang.

635
00:36:52,714 --> 00:36:55,434
The Herbal Encyclopedia
is far from enough.

636
00:36:56,954 --> 00:36:57,714
That's true.

637
00:36:58,954 --> 00:37:00,234
How can the Herbal Encyclopedia

638
00:37:00,355 --> 00:37:02,154
cure all diseases in the world?

639
00:37:02,914 --> 00:37:03,795
What if there were dozens

640
00:37:03,795 --> 00:37:04,835
of Herbal Encyclopedia?

641
00:37:09,914 --> 00:37:11,234
That's a good idea.

642
00:37:12,595 --> 00:37:13,115
No way.

643
00:37:13,634 --> 00:37:14,234
It's impossible.

644
00:37:14,914 --> 00:37:15,995
Our ancestor exhausted

645
00:37:16,355 --> 00:37:18,275
his effort for
only one Herbal Encyclopedia.

646
00:37:18,914 --> 00:37:19,674
Just tell me.

647
00:37:20,434 --> 00:37:21,714
Is this a good thing?

648
00:37:21,835 --> 00:37:22,954
Is it worth doing?

649
00:37:22,954 --> 00:37:24,595
Of course it is.

650
00:37:24,595 --> 00:37:26,275
Since you've affirmed its value,

651
00:37:26,355 --> 00:37:27,434
why don't you do it?

652
00:37:27,835 --> 00:37:29,515
Just because it's difficult

653
00:37:29,714 --> 00:37:30,714
and you dare not do it?

654
00:37:31,555 --> 00:37:32,795
Do your best.

655
00:37:33,355 --> 00:37:35,035
Even if it's only
100 more prescriptions,

656
00:37:35,315 --> 00:37:37,835
someone will benefit from them.

657
00:37:38,995 --> 00:37:39,632
Xiaoyao.

658
00:37:40,714 --> 00:37:42,035
Do whatever you want.

659
00:37:42,394 --> 00:37:43,634
I have your back.

660
00:37:44,634 --> 00:37:46,115
It may be somewhat difficult.

661
00:37:46,634 --> 00:37:48,075
But it can be done with the effort

662
00:37:48,674 --> 00:37:49,515
of an entire nation.

663
00:37:51,595 --> 00:37:52,355
Thank you, Xuan.

664
00:38:17,714 --> 00:38:19,755
Work on them tomorrow if you're tired.

665
00:38:20,634 --> 00:38:22,075
These medical records won't run away.

666
00:38:22,115 --> 00:38:23,355
There's plenty of time.

667
00:38:23,634 --> 00:38:24,674
You don't have to rush.

668
00:38:25,634 --> 00:38:27,434
I want to get these all sorted out

669
00:38:27,434 --> 00:38:28,795
before leaving Chenrong Mountain.

670
00:38:32,954 --> 00:38:34,194
Leaving Chenrong Mountain?

671
00:38:39,115 --> 00:38:39,835
But

672
00:38:40,434 --> 00:38:41,355
being with Jing

673
00:38:41,474 --> 00:38:44,154
might delay the process
of editing the book.

674
00:38:48,755 --> 00:38:49,275
Xiaoyao.

675
00:38:51,075 --> 00:38:52,154
Compiling medical books

676
00:38:52,154 --> 00:38:52,995
requires a great deal

677
00:38:52,995 --> 00:38:54,394
of manpower and resources

678
00:38:54,795 --> 00:38:57,434
as well as time and energy.

679
00:38:58,714 --> 00:39:00,355
If you become Lady of Tushan,

680
00:39:00,355 --> 00:39:02,275
you certainly won't be so free

681
00:39:02,874 --> 00:39:04,315
to communicate with physicians,

682
00:39:04,954 --> 00:39:06,835
and collect herbs from various places.

683
00:39:08,555 --> 00:39:10,035
Jing will surely support me.

684
00:39:12,474 --> 00:39:14,795
Even if Tushan Jing supports you,

685
00:39:15,835 --> 00:39:17,874
what about those elders
of the Tushan Family?

686
00:39:17,995 --> 00:39:19,755
They will keep a close eye on you

687
00:39:19,795 --> 00:39:21,315
to see if you live up to the title

688
00:39:21,355 --> 00:39:22,434
of Lady of Tushan.

689
00:39:23,434 --> 00:39:25,035
They may not support you.

690
00:39:25,595 --> 00:39:26,634
By then, Tushan Jing

691
00:39:26,755 --> 00:39:28,394
will be caught in a dilemma

692
00:39:28,755 --> 00:39:30,355
because of you and the elders.

693
00:39:33,275 --> 00:39:34,115
You are right.

694
00:39:34,555 --> 00:39:36,035
Jing always puts me first.

695
00:39:36,595 --> 00:39:38,275
I can't make him defend me

696
00:39:38,835 --> 00:39:40,634
and grow distant with those elders.

697
00:40:00,154 --> 00:40:01,035
Close your eyes.

698
00:40:01,795 --> 00:40:03,115
Open them when I tell you to.

699
00:40:03,595 --> 00:40:04,874
Why did you bring me here?

700
00:40:06,515 --> 00:40:07,275
Close your eyes.

701
00:40:09,115 --> 00:40:09,712
Okay.

702
00:40:16,674 --> 00:40:17,474
Watch your step.

703
00:40:30,394 --> 00:40:31,115
Are we ready?

704
00:40:31,234 --> 00:40:32,315
Open your eyes now.

705
00:40:41,595 --> 00:40:42,434
Rejuvenation Hall.

706
00:40:44,234 --> 00:40:44,874
Xiaoyao.

707
00:40:45,874 --> 00:40:47,075
I have something to tell you.

708
00:40:49,835 --> 00:40:50,394
- I...
- Jing.

709
00:40:51,634 --> 00:40:52,434
Thank you.

710
00:40:54,674 --> 00:40:55,555
If you agree,

711
00:40:56,154 --> 00:40:57,394
I should thank you.

712
00:40:57,555 --> 00:40:58,434
You must have

713
00:40:58,555 --> 00:40:59,874
brought me here to encourage me

714
00:41:00,595 --> 00:41:01,795
about compiling

715
00:41:01,795 --> 00:41:02,954
that medical book, right?

716
00:41:09,035 --> 00:41:09,584
Jing.

717
00:41:10,154 --> 00:41:10,835
Thank you.

718
00:41:11,474 --> 00:41:12,434
Compiling a medical book

719
00:41:12,515 --> 00:41:14,234
is going to take a lot of time

720
00:41:14,634 --> 00:41:15,835
and I'll have to travel.

721
00:41:16,634 --> 00:41:17,634
Our wedding

722
00:41:17,634 --> 00:41:18,714
will have to wait.

723
00:41:19,434 --> 00:41:21,434
I didn't know how to tell you.

724
00:41:22,515 --> 00:41:24,035
But you already knew.

725
00:41:24,595 --> 00:41:25,795
And you're so supportive.

726
00:41:30,704 --> 00:41:32,464
♪You are the warm sun♪

727
00:41:32,464 --> 00:41:35,856
♪That opens the window to darkness♪

728
00:41:36,880 --> 00:41:42,032
♪Removing the confusion♪

729
00:41:43,508 --> 00:41:45,456
♪You are the flowers♪

730
00:41:45,456 --> 00:41:48,976
♪That bloom with the fragrance of life♪

731
00:41:49,634 --> 00:41:50,555
What's wrong?

732
00:41:55,995 --> 00:41:56,714
Xiaoyao.

733
00:41:57,674 --> 00:41:58,755
Compiling a medical book

734
00:41:59,275 --> 00:42:01,394
and practicing medical skills
can benefit the people.

735
00:42:01,835 --> 00:42:02,835
If you want to do it,

736
00:42:03,434 --> 00:42:04,595
I will totally support you.

737
00:42:07,434 --> 00:42:08,634
The Tushan Family's caravan

738
00:42:08,674 --> 00:42:09,874
travels around all year

739
00:42:10,315 --> 00:42:11,714
and knows many places.

740
00:42:12,035 --> 00:42:14,035
The physicians
can set out with the caravan

741
00:42:14,234 --> 00:42:16,075
to collect prescriptions and herbs.

742
00:42:16,434 --> 00:42:17,755
It's both safe and efficient.

743
00:42:21,595 --> 00:42:22,194
Jing.

744
00:42:23,035 --> 00:42:24,394
Why are you so nice?

745
00:42:29,115 --> 00:42:30,394
The person I love is nice.

746
00:42:31,194 --> 00:42:32,795
That's why I'm eager to do better.

747
00:42:33,296 --> 00:42:35,568
♪You are no longer alone♪

748
00:42:36,208 --> 00:42:40,912
♪And I am no longer sorrowful♪

749
00:42:42,036 --> 00:42:48,048
♪Along with you, I can bloom♪

750
00:42:49,268 --> 00:42:54,672
♪And grow♪

751
00:43:19,098 --> 00:43:22,330
♪Looking back on my old days♪

752
00:43:23,616 --> 00:43:27,898
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

753
00:43:29,978 --> 00:43:34,778
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

754
00:43:37,914 --> 00:43:40,186
♪Only emptiness remained♪

755
00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:46,202
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

756
00:43:48,051 --> 00:43:52,442
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

757
00:43:53,978 --> 00:43:59,451
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

758
00:44:00,402 --> 00:44:06,234
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

759
00:44:09,082 --> 00:44:13,818
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

760
00:44:15,130 --> 00:44:19,642
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

761
00:44:21,082 --> 00:44:27,034
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

762
00:44:27,811 --> 00:44:32,122
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

763
00:44:33,114 --> 00:44:38,080
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

764
00:44:39,072 --> 00:44:43,680
♪All is bleak without you♪

765
00:44:45,018 --> 00:44:50,624
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

766
00:44:51,738 --> 00:45:02,752
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪
